Preheat oven at 325 degrees F. In medium bowl, combine apples, EAGLE BRAND(R) and cinnamon. In large bowl, cut 1/2 cup butter into 1 cup biscuit mix until crumbly. Stir in apple mixture. Pour into ungreased 9-inch square baking pan. In small bowl, combine remaining 1/2 cup biscuit mix and brown sugar; cut in remaining 2 tablespoons butter until crumbly. Add nuts. Sprinkle evenly over apple mixture. Bake 1 hour or until golden brown. Serve warm with ice cream or whipped topping (optional). Store leftovers covered in refrigerator.